{"tid":339731,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好煩。好攰，好灰呀！！！！！","createTime":"2017-07-29T09:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T10:20:50.000Z","uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"912c5dab497a9dff05cc9c68124287bd4316dcf2","tid":339731,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T09:58:39.000Z","msg":"之前都好地地，見到人可以傾到幾句，上堂都會識到幾個人去傾計咁。。<br />\n<br />\n依幾日無端端完全唔識得同人講嘢咁。要好勉強先同到人傾計，上堂或者有event嗰時。覺得個個人都好煩，見到其他人嘅面口好憎佢地，就算有人肯同我傾，但係我個腦好似空左咁完全無力去延續到對話。有傾開嘅又唔太想搵，搵左又覺得佢地好煩。但係唔搵又覺得好孤獨。個人好似有啲壓抑住，但係又釋放唔到。。好辛苦。。。。"},{"pid":"643e12f83513d2b67aa86ab37ad11e1ebab58e7f","tid":339731,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:13:36.000Z","msg":"枝枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f1376005f9549baee30772ce29883095dabb48","tid":339731,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>枝枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夏夏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}